THE FOLLOWING GRAPH DEMONSTRATES A FIVE-YEAR COMPARISON OF CUMULATIVE TOTAL RETURNS FOR NIKES CLASS B COMMON STOCK, THE STANDARD & POORS 500 STOCK INDEX, THE STANDARD & POORS

