THIS SCHEDULE IS INTENDED TO SATISFY THE QUANTITATIVE RECONCILIATION FOR NON-GAAP FINANCIAL MEASURES IN ACCORDANCE WITH REGULATION G AND ITEM 10(E) OF

REGULATION S-K OF THE SECURITIES AND EXCHANGE COMMISSION. IN ADDITION, THIS SCHEDULE IS PROVIDED TO ENHANCE THE VISIBILITY OF THE UNDERLYING BUSINESS TRENDS EXCLUDING THESE NON-COMPARABLE ITEMS FOR THE YEARS ENDED MAY 31, 2009 AND 2008.

