DEPRECIATION AND AMORTIZATION RELATED TO THE COMPANYS CORPORATE HEADQUARTERS, UNALLOCATED INSURANCE AND BENEFIT PROGRAMS, FOREIGN CURRENCY GAINS AND LOSSES, INCLUDING HEDGE GAINS AND LOSSES, CORPORATE ELIMINATIONS AND OTHER ITEMS.

