PROGRAM WILL COMMENCE UPON COMPLETION OF OUR CURRENT $3 BILLION SHARE REPURCHASE PROGRAM. WE EXPECT TO FUND SHARE REPURCHASES FROM OPERATING CASH FLOW, EXCESS CASH, AND/OR DEBT. THE TIMING AND THE AMOUNT OF SHARES PURCHASED WILL BE DICTATED BY OUR

CAPITAL NEEDS AND STOCK MARKET CONDITIONS.

