WE GENERALLY ORDER PRODUCT AT LEAST FOUR TO FIVE MONTHS IN ADVANCE OF SALE BASED PRIMARILY ON ADVANCED FUTURES ORDERS RECEIVED FROM CUSTOMERS. THE AMOUNTS LISTED

