THE 1990 PLAN. THE NUMBER OF SHARES GRANTED TO EMPLOYEES DURING THE YEARS ENDED MAY 31, 2009, 2008 AND 2007 WERE 75,000, 110,000 AND 345,000 WITH WEIGHTED AVERAGE VALUES PER SHARE OF $56.97, $59.50 AND $39.38, RESPECTIVELY. RECIPIENTS OF

